CTRL --> shift the pointer between the host and the guest while using the virtual machine
CRTL + R --> enable reverse index search in the terminal for command history
LCTRL + L --> clear the screen, just giving a new page in the terminal by keeping all the session history
CTRL + C --> end the current command or process
TAB --> use the auto completion for the commands or files
TAB TAB --> view all the available targets for auto completion
CTRL + D --> to close the terminal 
CTRL + ALT + T --> to opena a new terminal

